      "html": "<h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of fragment 'a' after IGPalermo and photograph; text of fragment 'b' after Gualtherus and Kaibel, and requiring further revision</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"b.1\">b.1: <span>Kaibel: ἔχει[ν ἐ]πόθησεν</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"b.3-4\">b.3-4: <span>Gualtherus: ΛΥΓΡΟΙϹ Μ . . . |ΜΑΤΑ; Torremuzza et al.: ὄμ-|ματα</span></span><br></li><li><span class=\"b.4\">b.4: <span>Gualtherus: ΜΥΡΟΜΕΝϹ . . ; Torremuzza: μυρομένη</span></span></li></ul>"
